1
00:00:05,714 --> 00:00:07,633
OHILA: He has asked to see you.

2
00:00:08,217 --> 00:00:10,677
His servants seek you everywhere.

3
00:00:11,595 --> 00:00:13,138
-Will you go?
-DOCTOR: No.

4
00:00:13,639 --> 00:00:15,098
Why do you always lie?

5
00:00:15,182 --> 00:00:18,977
-Why do you always assume I'm lying?
-It saves time. The truth.

6
00:00:19,102 --> 00:00:20,729
-Will you go?
-No.

7
00:00:20,812 --> 00:00:22,523
-When?
-Soon.

8
00:00:24,983 --> 00:00:26,109
Why?

9
00:00:27,778 --> 00:00:29,446
-Did something happen?
-No.

10
00:00:29,863 --> 00:00:31,073
Was it recent?

11
00:00:34,243 --> 00:00:35,702
Yes.

12
00:00:35,994 --> 00:00:39,915
Whatever it was,
you owe that creature nothing.

13
00:00:39,998 --> 00:00:42,626
He and I have known each other
a long time.

14
00:00:42,709 --> 00:00:44,920
You've been enemies for all of it.

15
00:00:45,003 --> 00:00:47,339
An enemy is just a friend
you don't really know yet.

16
00:00:47,422 --> 00:00:49,925
Sorry, was that me being cynical again?

17
00:00:50,008 --> 00:00:51,802
Aren't we friends, Doctor?

18
00:00:52,219 --> 00:00:53,804
That's different. I don't like you.

19
00:00:53,971 --> 00:00:57,099
(CHUCKLES) Which means you can trust me.

20
00:01:00,978 --> 00:01:03,355
-You know who to give that to.
-(SIGHS)

21
00:01:07,859 --> 00:01:11,863
I won't go straight away.
I'll hang out for a bit.

22
00:01:13,740 --> 00:01:17,411
Probably meditate on a rock somewhere.

23
00:01:18,328 --> 00:01:19,788
Get myself ready.

24
00:01:19,871 --> 00:01:23,166
You are embarking on an enterprise
that will end in your destruction.

25
00:01:23,709 --> 00:01:25,752
You can say that I'm being born.

26
00:01:26,128 --> 00:01:27,713
Wherever you go,

27
00:01:28,338 --> 00:01:30,841
there are people
who care enough to find you.

28
00:01:32,801 --> 00:01:34,761
Look after the universe for me.

29
00:01:35,095 --> 00:01:36,513
I've put a lot of work into it.

30
00:01:38,348 --> 00:01:40,892
Anyone can hide from an enemy, Doctor...

31
00:01:41,310 --> 00:01:43,395
No one from a friend.

32
00:01:45,564 --> 00:01:47,566
(THUNDER CRACKS)

